  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    A class for storing the user's account information.
    Answer
    This is a model class for answers Answers consists of a body, user, list of replies, rating, date and number of replies Answer can also consist of a Photo, if it is attached
    AnswerSorter
    This class is used to sort an Answer List by various fields, it is primarily used for the Sort function on the app pages that allow for sorting.
    ApplicationState
    A static class used for managing the application's data in its current state.
    Geolocation
    Geolocation is used for locating the current postion of the user
    OfflineAnswer  
    Question
    This is a model class for questions Question consists of a title, body, username, list of replies, list of answers, date and rating Question can also consist of a Photo, if a photo is attached
    QuestionSorter
    This class is used to sort an Question List by various fields, it is primarily used for the Sort function on the app pages that allow for sorting.
    Reply
    This class is our model for replies replies consists of a body, author, and date implemented.
    ReplySorter
    This class is used to sort an Reply List by various fields, it is primarily used for the Sort function on the app pages that allow for sorting.
    SaveManager
    Handles local saving and loading.
